<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/><expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> τῆς γεούχου Παπνουθίῳ 

    <lb n="2"/><expan>προ<ex cert="high">νοητῇ</ex></expan> καὶ Ἁτρῇ <expan>φρ<ex cert="high">οντιστῇ</ex></expan> <expan>χ<ex cert="high">αίρειν</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="3"/><choice><corr>σπουδάσατε</corr><sic>σουδασαται</sic></choice> τὸν ταυρε-

    <lb n="4"/>λάτην μετὰ τῶν μόσχων 

    <lb n="5"/>καὶ τοῦ ζυγοῦ καὶ <expan>σχοινίω<ex cert="high">ν</ex></expan> 

    <lb n="6"/>αὐτῶν <choice><corr>ἐξελάσαι</corr><sic>εξελασε</sic></choice> ἐν τῇ 

    <lb n="7"/>σήμερον εἰς τὸ ἡμέτερον 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐποίκιον Ἀκινδύνου πρὸ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ς</unclear> 

    <lb n="9"/>σ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ύ</unclear>ρσιν λίθου τῶν κυρί-

    <lb n="10"/>ων μου ἀδελφῶν Νεπω-

    <lb n="11"/>τιανοῦ καὶ Διογένους· οἴδα-

    <lb n="12"/>τε καὶ <choice><corr>ὑμεῖς</corr><sic>υμις</sic></choice> ὅτι οὔκ <choice><corr>εἰσιν</corr><sic>ισιν</sic></choice> ξέ-

    <lb n="13"/>νοι. ἀλλὰ πα´ντως ἐν 

    <lb n="14"/>τῇ σήμερον, ἐπειδὴ συν-

    <lb n="15"/>έθεντο βαστάξαι ἐν τῇ 

    <lb n="16"/><choice><corr>κυριακῇ</corr><sic>κυριακην</sic></choice> ἡμέρᾳ, τουτ-

    <lb n="17"/>έστιν αὔριον <num value="11">ια</num>. 

    <lb n="18"/>μὴ οὖν, ἀδελφοί, δόξητε 

    <lb n="19"/><choice><corr>ἀμελῆσαι</corr><sic>αμελησε</sic></choice> καὶ ἐνεδρευθῇ 

    <lb n="20"/>τὸ ἔργον τῶν ἀνθρώ-

    <lb n="21"/>πων, <choice><corr>ἐμοὶ</corr><sic>εμεναν</sic></choice> δὲ οὐκ ὀλί-

    <lb n="22"/>γην ὕβριν προσηνέγκα-

    <lb n="23"/>τε. περὶ δὲ τοῦ τροχοῦ 

    <lb n="24"/>ἀρκετοί ἐστε. ἐν τῇ αὔριον 

    <lb n="25"/>ὁ ἀδελφὸς Λούκιος ἀπαντᾷ 

    <lb n="26"/>πρὸς ὑμᾶς. </ab></div><div n="meta.33717" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.33717" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="301" notAfter="400">IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.33717" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Gehört zum Archiv der Brüder Papnuthis und Dorotheos. Vgl. New Docs 9, 2002, S. 106-118.</p></div><div n="meta.33717" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.33717" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3407</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">33717</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3407</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;48;3407" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.33717" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">270</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">202</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">153</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33717" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.33717" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en" default="NO"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Bagnall - Cribiore, Women's Letters (2006), S. 215</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33717" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.33717" type="figure" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASHf784059df982224b461cb3"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>